= LINZ Geodetic modules

The Geodetic modules provide tools for converting between different coordinate
systems in use in New Zealand.  The coordinate systems are loaded a coordinate
system definition file, by default installed at a location defined by the 
COORDSYSDEF environment variable.

Copyright 2014 Crown copyright (c) Land Information New Zealand and the New
Zealand Government.

== Dependencies

 * Perl 5.88 or greater, plus
    - Time::JulianDay

== Compatibility

Tested on Windows XP and Server 2003, and Ubuntu 10.4 (Lucid)

== Install

This is a pure perl implementation of coordinate conversions.  Installation
uses the Module::Build process listed below. 

-- Simple install

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build install	
